title: Trump website goes down during debate
text:
Trump website goes down during debate
It was back up shortly after 9:30 p.m.
Story Continued Below
The outage appeared to begin shortly after both Trump and his Democratic rival Hillary Clinton encouraged viewers to visit their website for details of their policies.
The hacktivist group Anonymous tweeted a few minutes prior that it was "getting things set up" for the debate, but it was unclear exactly what the tweet was in reference to.
Anonymous has taken down Trump's website before.
